    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "There's no update on this yet. The hierarchical menu behavior currently relies heavily on the expected DOM output, which does not ensure that it will work with any custom templates.\r\n\r\nWe will let you know in this thread if/when we plan on addressing this issue. As @Haroenv suggested, using a connector is the best way to handle these edge cases.",
