    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "Only one selection will be possible, this is an underlying limitation in the helper code for hierarchical menus, to which we are aware. It seems like we have no issue open in InstantSearch.js, but we have an open issue you can upvote on React InstantSearch: https://github.com/algolia/react-instantsearch/issues/24",
